), 
<collectingCountry id="F334760FFFC2C168FCAD778724A47ED5" box="[804,945,1232,1258]" name="Guadeloupe" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Guadeloupe</collectingCountry>
and Les Saintes (present study). Probably occurs also in the Mediterranean, as illustrated by the sample 
